RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT PRODUCT_CODE, PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT WHERE MODULE IN ('OL','LB','FC') AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND ONCE_AUTH = 'Y' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' ORDER BY PRODUCT_CODE
SELECT STATUS FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_STATUS_MASTER WHERE PRODUCT = ?
SELECT TRN_CODE, TRN_DESC FROM OLTMS_TRN_CODE WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND ONCE_AUTH = 'Y'

RAD_DATASOURCES.DEFAULT_WHERE: PRODUCT IN (SELECT PRODUCT FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_STATUS_MASTER) AND STATUS IN (SELECT STATUS FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_STATUS_MASTER)

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT AC_GL_NO , AC_GL_DESC FROM OLTB_ACCOUNT WHERE AC_OR_GL = 'G' AND AC_GL_REC_STATUS = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' ORDER BY GL_CATEGORY, AC_GL_NO

RAD_DATASOURCES.DEFAULT_WHERE: PRODUCT IN (SELECT PRODUCT FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_STATUS_MASTER)AND STATUS IN (SELECT STATUS FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_STATUS_MASTER)

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT A.MSG_TYPE, B.DESCRIPTION FROM OLTM_PRODUCT_EVENT_ADVICE A, OLTMS_MSG_TYPE B WHERE A.PRODUCT_CODE = ? AND A.MSG_TYPE = B.MSG_TYPE AND A.MSG_TYPE NOT IN (SELECT MESSAGE_CODE FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_STATUS_ADVICES WHERE PRODUCT = ? AND STATUS = ?) UNION SELECT MSG_TYPE, DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_MSG_TYPE C WHERE MODULE = 'OL' AND MSG_TYPE NOT IN (SELECT MESSAGE_CODE FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_STATUS_ADVICES WHERE PRODUCT = ? AND STATUS = ?)

SELECT ROLE_CODE, ROLE_DESCRIPTION ,MAP_TYPE FROM OLTBS_ACCROLE A, OLTMS_PRODUCT_ACCROLE B WHERE A.ROLE_CODE = B.ACCOUNTING_ROLE AND B.PRODUCT_CODE = ? AND B.STATUS = 'NORM' AND A.ALLOW_TRANSFER_GL = 'Y' AND A.MODULE = 'OL' AND ROLE_CODE NOT IN (SELECT ACCOUNT_ROLE FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_STATUS_GL WHERE PRODUCT = ? AND STATUS = ?)
SELECT AC_GL_NO, AC_GL_DESC FROM OLTB_ACCOUNT WHERE AC_OR_GL = 'G' AND AC_GL_REC_STATUS = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' ORDER BY GL_CATEGORY, AC_GL_NO
SELECT AC_GL_NO, AC_GL_DESC FROM OLTB_ACCOUNT WHERE AC_OR_GL = 'G' AND AC_GL_REC_STATUS = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' ORDER BY GL_CATEGORY, AC_GL_NO

SELECT * FROM (SELECT X.COMPONENT,X.COMPONENT_DESCRIPTION,X.PRODUCT FROM LFTMS_PRODUCT_ICCF X, LFTB_ICCF_RLAVL Y WHERE X.PRODUCT = ? AND X.RULE = Y.RULE_ID AND Y.RULE_TYPE = 'I' UNION SELECT 'PRINCIPAL', 'PRINCIPAL',? FROM DUAL) A WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_LIQ_ORDER B WHERE A.PRODUCT = B.PRODUCT AND B.COMPONENT = A.COMPONENT AND NVL(B.STATUS, 'NORM') = ?)

RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: OLTMS_PRODUCT_STATUS_GL.PRODUCT = OLTMS_PRODUCT_STATUS_RTH_EXPR.PRODUCT_CODE AND OLTMS_PRODUCT_STATUS_GL.ACCOUNT_ROLE = OLTMS_PRODUCT_STATUS_RTH_EXPR.ACCOUNTING_ROLE AND OLTMS_PRODUCT_STATUS_GL.STATUS = OLTMS_PRODUCT_STATUS_RTH_EXPR.STATUS

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT AC_GL_NO FROM OLTB_ACCOUNT WHERE AC_OR_GL = 'G' AND AC_GL_REC_STATUS = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' ORDER BY GL_CATEGORY, AC_GL_NO

SELECT DISTINCT sde_id FROM (SELECT sde_id FROM oltms_sde WHERE sde_id NOT IN ('OVR_DAYS','LOAN_STATUS') UNION select 'PRINCIPAL' || '_OVR_DAYS' SDE_ID from dual UNION select component || '_OVR_DAYS' SDE_ID from lftm_product_iccf where product = ? and SHOWN_IN_CONTRACT_MAIN_SCREEN = 'Y')
